snippet.title: Rise of the Stikeez Trailer
snippet.description:
Help the Stickeez find their way to their friends!Help them explore this strange new land as they gather themselves and rise up to the challenges that come their way!

Rise of the Stickeez is a puzzle platform game; help these three Stickeez gather their lost friends throughout 60 Levels, with various challenges and hazards that stand in their way.

Use power ups to help you find your friends, overcome obstacles and survive the dangers of being a Stickeez in such a huge place.

Features: 
60 puzzled filled levels
6 unique environments to explore
Intuitive and simple controls
Engaging music to get you going
An absolute Stickee blast

Download for Free the Rise of the Stikeez Game App!

https://itunes.apple.com/ph/app/id820867041 - English
